{"product_id": "39160", "page": 3, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-12-03", "text": "Single Player: Couldn't get into it though because I really wanted to do the co-op. I have not completed or beaten the game because it cannot hold my interest (and that says A LOT).\nMultiplayer: Co-op is garbage due to camera issues, however there is a community mod that fixes the camera issue making the game actually playable in co-op. The problem was getting my friends interested in downloading it again because we spent a whole of 20 minutes before we decided we did NOT wish to play anymore.\nConclusion: if you can get it on sale for cheap, by all means. single player makes it worth spending an hour or more. don't expect too much more than that.", "hours": 13.1, "user_id": "76561197993531965", "username": "Pikas Pilate", "products": 250, "early_access": false}
