{"product_id": "39160", "page": 5, "page_order": 1, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-10-01", "text": "Played the original Dungeon Siege, really liked it. Got this game, took me a bit to get into it, but its still decent, other than a LOT shorter and less open world than DS1 was.", "hours": 40.0, "username": "Halogen3", "products": 180, "early_access": false}
