{"product_id": "39160", "page": 6, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2017-09-18", "text": "Well, that was depressing.\nPros:\n+ Story (what I saw of it) loked good, if a bit generic.\n+ Graphics are nice.\n+ Music is nice.\nCons:\n- Multiplayer co-op does NOT ALLOW SECONDARY PLAYERS TO KEEP PROGRESS OR ITEMS.\n- Multiplayer shares inventory. Completely.\n--- Camera controls are absolute. Crap. They'd be better off without camera control.\n- Mouse and keyboard controls are terrible.\n- Gamepad controls DO NOT ALL WORK. Even with gamepad, you will have to use mouse and keyboard for SOME things.\n- Multiplayer mode allows the appearance of voting on some things, but it does not work, and only the host player will appear in the story or cutscenes.", "hours": 1.0, "user_id": "76561198021304152", "username": "flameskitten", "products": 484, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
