{"product_id": "39160", "page": 11, "page_order": 8, "recommended": true, "date": "2017-03-17", "text": "For a game that was released 6 years ago I was really surprised at how good it is. I haven't played a good RPG in a long time and this one hit the spot. Good story line with good voice overs and some reallly nice graphics. I played it on my Acer Aspire V17 gaming laptop with a  Windows  X box One  USB controller.  Gaming controller worked perfect.", "hours": 61.8, "user_id": "76561198334759464", "username": "prezba29", "products": 48, "early_access": false}
