{"product_id": "39160", "page": 15, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-12-26", "text": "It's fun, but it has some drawbacks\nIf you cant get over the crappy camera and the occasional super hard boss its a good game\nI say buy it when its on sale, and check it out", "hours": 1.5, "compensation": "Product received for free", "username": "Suicidal Sandwich", "products": 139, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39160", "page": 15, "page_order": 7, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-12-25", "text": "This game is bad and the Devs should feel bad. I personally love Dungeon Siege, but this 3rd installment was terrible. The gameplay wasn't there for me, and the camera was god awful..I can't even. I do not recommend this game at all. Totally thumbs down from me. I know I don't show much play time for this title but that's because it didn't take long for me to realize this was terrible. For the most part..it's mostly the camera..it's so bad...ugh.", "hours": 1.2, "username": "Dread Xanthis", "products": 126, "found_funny": 1, "early_access": false}
