{"product_id": "39160", "page": 16, "page_order": 3, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-12-04", "text": "Worst game I ever played. No, wait, that's reserved for the new Neverwinter. Sorry. Bought this game in 2014, played 19 minutes. To say i didn't like it would be a major understatement. I just hate when game makers design a game and make the controls cumbersome, awkward, and impossible. Reminds me of the Witcher, another failure.", "hours": 0.3, "user_id": "76561198055195397", "username": "GhoWriter", "products": 2, "early_access": false}
