{"product_id": "39160", "page": 17, "page_order": 4, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-24", "text": "Dungeon Siege 3 is one of the games with is underrated because it has a good storyline and has very more to it then you think because not only is it a hack and slash game but it is also a role play game because a lot of your decision you made has a great impack in you game later on. so I wil say go buy it especially when it is as now on sale for 75% less then the normal and if you think about it buy the collection edition because you will get a lot more for the money or if you only will play the third so at least buy the DLC for it for you will get more for the money.\nAnd for the record I have alredy finish the game and collected and see what there is to it but I am going to play it again because it is a good game.", "hours": 36.1, "user_id": "76561198007118224", "username": "delta rygskyder", "products": 102, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39160", "page": 17, "page_order": 5, "recommended": false, "date": "2016-11-23", "text": "This is, without a doubt, one of the WORST action RPGs I have ever played and a travesty to the Dungeon Siege name.  Do NOT buy this game, it is unoriginal, plays like a gauntlet legends clone with terrible interaction w/ the environment and after dying to the same boss for 20 minutes in an absolutely LINEAR RPG experience w/i the first hour of gameplay, I would rather mutilate my genitals than play this game.  This game needs to go die in a dumpster fire.", "hours": 1.1, "user_id": "76561198094809808", "username": "rhadamsjr84", "products": 81, "found_funny": 2, "early_access": false}
{"product_id": "39160", "page": 17, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2016-11-21", "text": "Very nice game!\nI recommend grabbing 1 buddy and play through this. It offers a good challenge for everyone if you pick the right difficulty.\nHas good rpg-elements and a well designed battle system.\nStory is alright but not really great.\nIt takes 20-30h to complete.\nDefinitely worth it!", "hours": 23.0, "user_id": "76561197991681312", "username": "Zantis", "products": 310, "early_access": false}
