{"product_id": "39160", "page": 29, "page_order": 9, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-12-19", "text": "Hashtag: Notmydungeonsiege. I didn't know what to expect exactly, but this wasn't it. I might give it another try someday, but this one pretty much lost me in the first hour or two and looking back on it, I don't remember much of anything of the story, which is a shame because I can still remember the (utterly superfluous) plot of II pretty clearly.", "hours": 6.8, "user_id": "76561197979173524", "username": "Korentin Black", "products": 342, "early_access": false}
