{"product_id": "39160", "page": 31, "page_order": 1, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-11-29", "text": "Such a super extrem dissapoint ment the Dungeon Siege series (I , II) was soo awesome i simple couldent get enough from then and now comes dis. i think the dvelopers tryed to copy Diablo III for real there is almost no differens and the game sucks soo boring to play no pent only one companion... no that you can be awesome on all classes no sersly this game is just a copy of Diablo III im soo really dissapointet ment i just wasted my money on this.... soo sad they dident make it like dungeon siege 1 and made ethat one with awesome grapics omg that would be awesome. Soo what im gona do start a new search for games like Dungeon SIege II, I becose the 3 sersly sucks most boring game and i waset so hard myy time i spent in it", "hours": 19.1, "user_id": "76561198082631001", "username": "TheHaluzer (GER/CZ/SK)", "products": 50, "early_access": false}
