{"product_id": "39160", "page": 37, "page_order": 6, "recommended": true, "date": "2015-07-27", "text": "i find that it strays from the path of dungeon siege and if you played the first and second ones you know what i mean, i mean sure this is made by a diffrent dev studio but still they could have at least kept the large partys and made it so you were not a grand hero right off the start of the game i mean normally you start off as a merc, farmer, or child whose parents where killed when they went off to save the world guy that just gets asked to help out with normal stuff every so often, i find that the game is fun but not my cup 'o' tea", "hours": 5.1, "user_id": "76561198031712937", "username": "_-UT-_ S.W.A.T", "products": 273, "early_access": false}
