{"product_id": "39160", "page": 47, "page_order": 0, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-02-06", "text": "This is one of the worst, if not THE worst, game I have ever played. The UI, player controls, and camera controls are an abominable mess. I might have 45 minutes invested in this game and refused to waste another second. LOVED Dungeon Siege II back in the day, but this game is a travesty. Just glad I only paid a $1.99 for it. Yuck!", "hours": 1.7, "user_id": "76561198055646231", "username": "armorchick", "products": 32, "early_access": false}
