{"product_id": "39160", "page": 47, "page_order": 2, "recommended": false, "date": "2015-02-05", "text": "no, no, no, oh god no.\ndungeon siege III is very poor attempt at an rpg with the dungeon siege name slapped on it.\nThe camera system is nearly locked in place, leading to you not seeing enemys.\nthe comat system feel very clunky and delayed, with one click per attack with no option to simply hold the button.\nthe loot system is a bunch of differently named items with the exact same stats just to up numbers of loot.\nwhere in the previous titles you could build your own character, in this you are locked to 4 choices.\n\nnot worth the 3$ sale price", "hours": 0.7, "user_id": "76561197972683065", "username": "That faggot ass dog esquire", "products": 220, "early_access": false}
